<div style="BORDER-BOTTOM: #bdb5a3 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: #bdb5a3 1px solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 5px; PADDING-LEFT: 5px; PADDING-RIGHT: 5px; BACKGROUND: #e2d6bc; BORDER-TOP: #bdb5a3 1px solid; BORDER-RIGHT: #bdb5a3 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 5px">　本文由<span style="COLOR: #ff0000">巴士小编整理</span>投稿，并不代表巴士的观点。如果你有不同观点或想法要发表，请发布在巴士梦幻西游2论坛[<a href="http://dou.tgbus.com/forum-206-1.html"><font color="#0000ff"><u>点击投稿</u></font></a>]，相关负责人会推荐到专区首页，招聘梦幻论坛版主，联系QQ群：<font color="#ff0000">287105729</font>。</div>
<p>　　出凌波城这个门派的时候，我就从天宫转到了凌波城。到现在已经彻底的算是凌波城中的一员了。</p>
<p>　　废话不多说。先上图片。有图有真相　</p>
<p align="center"><img onload="resizepic(this)" onmousewheel="return bbimg(this)" border="0" hspace="0" alt="" src="http://img2.tgbusdata.cn/v2/thumb/jpg/OTBDLDYwMCwyNDAsNCwzLDEsLTEsMCx0cjY1/u/xyq.tgbus.com/UploadFiles_7209/201403/2014031117035524.jpg"><br><br><img onload="resizepic(this)" onmousewheel="return bbimg(this)" border="0" hspace="0" alt="" src="http://img2.tgbusdata.cn/v2/thumb/jpg/MEUxLDYwMCwyNDAsNCwzLDEsLTEsMCx0cjY1/u/xyq.tgbus.com/UploadFiles_7209/201403/2014031117035509.jpg"><br><br><img onload="resizepic(this)" onmousewheel="return bbimg(this)" border="0" hspace="0" alt="" src="http://img2.tgbusdata.cn/v2/thumb/jpg/MEU3LDYwMCwyNDAsNCwzLDEsLTEsMCx0cjY1/u/xyq.tgbus.com/UploadFiles_7209/201403/2014031117035587.jpg"><br></p>
